OL,3,CHorizon scandal victims who never saw
OL,4,Cjustice before death
OL,6,FITV News Correspondent Geraint Vincent
OL,7,Fheard from three families for whom the
OL,8,Ftruth can only repair some of the
OL,9,Fdamage
OL,11,FThe terrible miscarriage of justice at
OL,12,Fthe heart of the scandal is only some
OL,13,Fof the way to being put right.
OL,15,FHundreds of people are still waiting
OL,16,Ffor their criminal convictions to be
OL,17,Foverturned, many more are yet to
OL,18,Freceive compensation for the
OL,19,Flivelihoods they lost.
