OL,3,CHorizon scandal victims who never saw
OL,4,Cjustice before death
OL,6,FBut there are some victims of the
OL,7,Fscandal who will never know the relief
OL,8,Fof having their name cleared, the
OL,9,Fstigma officially washed away. They
OL,10,Fare the people who died before justice
OL,11,Fwas done.
OL,13,FBill Quarm was a sub-postmaster who
OL,14,Fhad his conviction for embezzlement
OL,15,Foverturned last year. He died of
OL,16,Fcancer in 2012.
OL,18,FAsk his widow, Anne, what effect the
OL,19,Fconviction had on him and her answer
OL,20,Fis short, simple and devastating. "It
OL,21,Fdestroyed him," she says.
