OL,6,FPeter Holmes took over a post office
OL,7,Fin Newcastle after a career spent in
OL,8,Fthe police force. To avoid going to
OL,9,Fjail, he pleaded guilty to false
OL,10,Faccounting in 2010.
OL,12,FHis conviction was quashed in 2021,
OL,13,Fsix years after his death. His widow
OL,14,FMarion describes his gradual decline
OL,15,Fas he was lost to his family. "He just
OL,16,Fturned in on himself," she says.
