OL,6,FSome compensation has been received
OL,7,Fand the Post Office says it is working
OL,8,Fas fast as it can to make payments to
OL,9,Fpeople who have been waiting many
OL,10,Fyears for justice.
OL,12,FBut what amount of money can
OL,13,Fcompensate a family life ruined by a
OL,14,Fwrongful conviction? What restitution
OL,15,Fcan be made to someone who died before
OL,16,Fjustice was done? Some wounds can
OL,17,Fnever heal.
